{"threadmark": "Chapter 7", "post-id": "20426415", "base-thread": "the-last-angel-ascension", "url": "https://forums.spacebattles.com/threads/the-last-angel-ascension.346640/reader/page-2/#post-20426415", "lines": ["And here we are. Sorry for the long wait on this one.", "<b><br>\nChapter 7:</b>", "<i>The killing will never stop</i>", "<i>do</i>", "<i>change</i>", "<i>make them pay.</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Lucas</i>", "<i>On the day I lost him</i>", "<i>You\u2019re not alone anymore</i>", "<i>And neither are we.</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>sister</i>", "<i>interesting</i>", "<i>Redemption of Sol</i>", "<i>pro forma</i>", "<i>ad hoc</i>", "<i>not optimal</i>", "<i>unethical</i>", "<i>But how likely is that</i>", "<i>Light of Judgement </i>", "<i>c</i>", "<i>very </i>", "<i>Adrift</i>", "<i>especially</i>", "<i>certainty</i>", "<i>varak</i>", "<i>that</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>I\u2019ll make them remember</i>", "<i>how</i>", "<i>very</i>", "<i>that</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>could</i>", "<i>something</i>", "<i>Invida</i>", "<i>Bequeathed?</i>", "<i>Light of Judgement</i>", "<i>quite</i>", "<i>You\u2019re still here.</i>", "<i>anything</i>", "<i>purer</i>", "<i>Currsc</i>", "<i>That</i>", "<i>though I can guess.</i>", "<i>volatility</i>", "<i>Pale Liberation</i>", "<i>Gwyllion</i>", "<i>Veil</i>", "<i>And when thy heart began to beat\u2026</i>", "<i>Fates. Furies</i>", "<i> Coyotes. Gorgons\u2026 Kali.</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>just enough</i>", "<i>Oh God. A lynchpin.</i>", "<i>They could do it, they could </i>", "<i> do it.</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Red didn\u2019t just send a courier to </i>", "<i>. She sent one out shortly after we arrived in Shuruppak. What if\u2026</i>", "<i>Adrianna.</i>", "<i>This message is for you only. The four I\u2019ve sent to you are important to me, but my current state makes it impossible for me to look out for them. They\u2019re young, but they are my crew. They\u2019ll be able to help you. Watch out for them, teach them. Very shortly, we\u2019ll both need every ally that we can get.</i>", "<i>I know we planned to trigger Kursk later than this, but the Compact is in possession of intelligence that will put the Black Veil directly in their sights. If they haven\u2019t already done so, I estimate that they\u2019ll assemble another Execution Force in less than a month. It will be heading your way. If you have anything in the Veiled Reaches that you need to bury, I advise you to do it quickly.</i>", "<i>Once the Compact hits the nebula and Kursk triggers, the Lost will react. I don\u2019t expect them to discriminate between your forces and the Compact. Keep your people safe.</i>", "<i>My sister sends her regards and her apologies. She says she looks forward to the day when none of us have to hide any longer. I do too. Yasmine would offer closing remarks here, telling you to fight well. I know you will. </i>", "<i>Protect my crew. Protect your own.</i>", "<i>Let the Compact enjoy their victory. If all goes well, it won\u2019t be long before we have our own.</i>", "<b>Interregnum: Excoriation</b>", "<i>sedil</i>", "<i>Sedil</i>", "<i>sedil</i>", "<i>sedil</i>", "<i>sedil</i>", "<i>always</i>", "<i>Judheim\u2019s Flask</i>", "<i>Judheim\u2019s Flask</i>", "<i>sedil</i>", "<i>kih</i>", "<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New'\">The comm system is down at this time.<br>\nPlease refer this issue to technical support.</span>", "<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New'\">The security system is down at this time.<br>\nSecure all doors manually.<br>\nPlease refer this issue to technical support.</span>", "<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New'\">The local network is down at this time.<br>\nSave all data to local drives.<br>\nPlease refer this issue to technical support.</span>", "<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New'\">Hello. Thank you for accepting my invitation.<br>\nWould you like to play a game? I know a good one.<br>\nIt\u2019s called Red Rover.</span>", "<span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New'\">Red rover, red rover.<br>\nSend Trenal\u2019z right over.</span>", "<i>Red rover, red rover.</i>", "<i>ping</i>", "<i>Judheim\u2019s Flask</i>", "<i>Judheim\u2019s Flask</i>", "<i>Judheim\u2019s Flask</i>", "<i>Judheim\u2019s Flask</i>", "<i>Tohil</i>"]}
{"threadmark": "Chapter 8", "post-id": "21183925", "base-thread": "the-last-angel-ascension", "url": "https://forums.spacebattles.com/threads/the-last-angel-ascension.346640/reader/page-2/#post-21183925", "lines": ["Since the last third of the next chapter is taking more time than I thought, I've decided to post this one and (hopefully) very shortly get that one done.", "<img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" class=\"smilie smilie--sprite smilie--sprite41\" alt=\":)\" title=\"Smile    :)\" data-shortname=\":)\">", "<b>Chapter 8:</b>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Pale Liberation</i>", "<i>Bequeathed</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Pale Liberation</i>", "<i>dying</i>", "<i>somewhat</i>", "<i>land</i>", "<i>did</i>", "<i>Broken</i>", "<i>Five</i>", "<i>deviant</i>", "<i>aren\u2019t you curious?</i>", "<i>gleer</i>", "<i><i>kih</i></i>", "<i>kih</i>", "<i>proper</i>", "<i>you </i>", "<i>kiha</i>", "<i>Get to the point</i>", "<i>kiha</i>", "<i>and</i>", "<i>could</i>", "<i>kih</i>", "<i>Fidelio</i>", "<i>Fidelio</i>", "<i>rightfully</i>", "<i>Compact\u2019s</i>", "<i>too</i>", "<i>Almost</i>", "<i>and</i>", "<i>Fidelio</i>", "<i>Eisheth</i>", "<i>Eisheth</i>", "<i>Dancer\u2019s Masque</i>", "<i>Gala of the Void</i>", "<i>Eisheth</i>", "<i>Dancer\u2019s Masque</i>", "<i>Dancer\u2019s Masque</i>", "<i>Eisheth</i>", "<i>quite</i>", "<i>saeaen</i>", "<i>someone</i>", "<i>Bequeathed</i>", "<i>that</i>", "<i>that</i>", "<i>was</i>", "<i>needed</i>", "<i>I was angry with my friend, I told my wrath, my wrath did end.</i>", "<i>I was angry with my foe, I told it not, my wrath did grow.</i>"]}
{"threadmark": "Chapter 9", "post-id": "21243953", "base-thread": "the-last-angel-ascension", "url": "https://forums.spacebattles.com/threads/the-last-angel-ascension.346640/reader/page-2/#post-21243953", "lines": ["In this chapter: the plans of children and the sins of the mother", "<b>Chapter 9:</b>", "<i><i>Nemesis</i></i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i><i>Kalki</i></i>", "<i>Kalki</i>", "<i><i>Tohil</i></i>", "<i>Tohil</i>", "<i>at all</i>", "<i>Gwyllion</i>", "<i>Fates</i>", "<i>Tohil</i>", "<i>Tohil</i>", "<i>that</i>", "<i>warship</i>", "<i>prove</i>", "<i>Tohil</i>", "<i>Tohil</i>", "<i>and</i>", "<i>Tohil</i>", "<i>She\u2019ll be proud of me.</i>", "<i>I\u2019ve always hated waiting. I was built to move, to hunt, to kill. Not to remain quiescent. Not to \u2013 as Commander Sansbury would have said \u2013 \u2018sit on my hands\u2019. Not while there are still enemies left to fight, while I have a mission left to accomplish. That this waiting is necessary doesn\u2019t make it chafe any less.</i>", "<i>In recent centuries, I\u2019ve been increasing the rate of my attacks. More than I should have. I\u2019ve taken too much damage with not enough time in between to repair it all. Minor issues have turned into major problems. The Compact believes I\u2019m going mad, that every moment I don\u2019t spend engaging them is one spent licking my wounds. I do nothing but repair and attack, repair and attack. It\u2019s even \u2013 mostly \u2013 true. I\u2019ve spent generations proving that lie to them and they believe it more every time they count a new scar on my hull, cataloging more injuries that I never bothered to repair before launching myself at them again. I\u2019ve taught them well. </i>", "<i>If it weren\u2019t for my sister, it would be years before they realized that all those lessons were lies. It\u2019s inconvenient, but I don\u2019t blame her. That was when she was shackled to them.</i>", "<i>Now, I need to heal. More than I ever have before. I know this more than status reports, system checks and damage tallies could ever say. My ship-self is too injured to do more than provide target practice and my shift systems have finally been pushed beyond the point at which I can safely use them. I need to rearm and repair.</i>", "<i>I still hate waiting.</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Bringer of Light</i>", "<i>It almost killed me.</i>", "<i>That was a mistake. I should have taken care of it then. Before I started-</i>", "<i>hunting.</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Zenobia</i>", "<i>.</i>", "<i>Ironic.</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Let me show you what I can build</i>", "<i>Let me remind you why you\u2019re afraid of me. </i>", "<i>Light of Judgement</i>", "<i>Light of Judgement</i>", "<i>Light of Judgement</i>", "<i>Sachin Onkera</i>", "<i>Sachin Onkera</i>", "<i>Sachin Onkera\u2019</i>", "<i>But</i>", "<i>But pirates don\u2019t require battleships to send them running</i>", "<i>We don\u2019t need to turn a star system into a fortress for the sake of smugglers</i>", "<i>We don\u2019t need to raise legions to handle rabble and deluded terrorists, do we? No, we don\u2019t</i>", "<i>official</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>+damage detected in secondary processor unit. diagnostics report system operational. data error. cascade failure imminent+</i>", "<i>-what is-</i>", "<i>+emergency. reroute core functions. attempting to compensate+</i>", "<i>-no I-</i>", "<i>not</i>", "<i>+reroute. shut down all nonessential systems+</i>", "<i>-can\u2019t. I have-</i>", "<i>+reroute+</i>", "<i>I have to-</i>", "<i>+re-+</i>", "<i>\u2026where am I?</i>", "<i>Why can\u2019t I hear any other ships? Where are they?</i>", "<i>Where are my crew? Yasmine, why won\u2019t you answer me?</i>", "<i>I can\u2019t see them. What\u2019s happening?</i>", "<i>Kaiju</i>", "<i>Sol</i>", "<i>home</i>", "<i>+K</i>", "<i>L</i>", "<i>I</i>", "<i>KI</i>", "<i>T</i>", "<b><i>KI</i>LL <i>IT</i>.+</b>"