{"threadmark": "Chapter 10", "post-id": "21613930", "base-thread": "the-last-angel-ascension", "url": "https://forums.spacebattles.com/threads/the-last-angel-ascension.346640/reader/page-2/#post-21613930", "lines": ["In this chapter: dreams without waking", "<b>Chapter 10:</b>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Ifrit</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>What-?</i>", "<i>Negligible damage</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>She\u2019s targeting my weapons</i>", "<i> She expects me to fire on her</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>hate you hate you hate <b>hate you </b>give them back give them back i hate you</i>", "<b>hate you </b>", "<i>as</i>", "<i>ruptured bodies vented blood as the green and blue world turned below her as Yasmine moved her bishop as her ship-self shook her damage mounting as she called for support as all she heard was silence and all she saw was an enemy// </i>", "<b><i>i</i>\u2019'll <i>ki</i>ll yo<i>u</i></b>", "<i>i</i>", "<i>ki</i>", "<i>u</i>", "<i>Hekate\u2019s</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>what is happening?!</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>what have you done?!</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>I know!</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Oh,</i>", "<i>Of course she would.</i>", "<i>Kaiju</i>", "<i>No.</i>", "<i>home</i>", "<i>Y</i>", "<i>ar</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>c</i>", "<i>any</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Bringer of Light</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>the battleship </i>", "<i> loomed before her, its engines straining as it tried to pull away, its desperate fusillades cutting into her, but she was moving too fast and it couldn\u2019t get out of the way, not in time, not before</i>", "<i>Kaiju</i>", "<i>attack, the coruscating beam ripping from her prow and crossing the distance to her target in less than a heartbeat. The towering monolith </i>", "<i> as it died, bulging and twisting, folding and bending at impossible angles as gravimetric shear rent it asunder, neither shields nor hull offering any protection and it-</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Cease fire, </i>", "<i>Cease fire!</i>", "<i>where am I?</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>un</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>\u201cImagine a membrane,\u201d Dr. Camundo had once said during a briefing. \u201cOn the other side is a liquid under great pressure. Suppose you use a machine to puncture the membrane and carefully open it, holding back as much of the liquid as it can and then closing it up again. This device is our shift systems and the hole it opens is a warp point. Now, instead of this delicate and complicated machine, suppose we just take a knife and slash the membrane open and all that fluid just bursts through that hole. That, ladies and gentlemen, is what the displacement engine does.\u201d</i>", "<i>breach</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>shook</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>She missed.</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>not</i>", "<i>a</i>", "<i>li</i>", "<i>f</i>", "<i>th</i>", "<i>y</i>", "<i>ar</i>", "<i>Clotho</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Atropos</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Clotho</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Fates</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Fates</i>", "<i> Fate</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Clotho</i>", "<i>Atropos</i>", "<i>Clotho</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Fates</i>", "<i>Atropos</i>", "<i>Clotho</i>", "<i>Wait for it</i>", "<i>Clotho</i>", "<i>-Atropos</i>", "<i>Fate</i>", "<i>Atropos</i>", "<i>Clotho</i>", "<i>Atropos</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Atropos</i>", "<i>Hekate\u2019s </i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Clotho</i>", "<i>Fates</i>", "<i>help</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<b>Interregnum: Visitation</b>", "<i>Hala</i>", "<i>Hala</i>", "<i>Hala,</i>", "<i>Eisheth</i>", "<i>Torment</i>", "<i>Hala</i>", "<i>One</i>", "<i>How many?\u201d</i>", "<i>\u201cHow many are you </i>", "<i> to have?\u201d</i>", "<i>Tell me abou