g something that even these deadtone can't ignore&gt;<br>\n<br>\nThe Naiad pulsed eagerly as she felt her commander's intentions. She spun away into the darkness, ready to fulfill her part in the plan, ready to herald the Music of the Spears.<br>\n<br>\nA sensation that could have been called a smile ran through Crimson Eight's neural network as she turned her ship-self onto a new course, UECNS <i>Xakharia</i>'s dark grey form soon one with the void.</div>", "<b>Hunter's Chorus</b>", "<i>oh yes</i>", "<i>Scales of Truth</i>", "<i>Sitamun</i>", "<i>&lt;</i>", "<i>Sitamun</i>", "<i>true</i>", "<i>Xakharia</i>"]}
{"threadmark": "Chapter 14", "post-id": "25131841", "base-thread": "the-last-angel-ascension", "url": "https://forums.spacebattles.com/threads/the-last-angel-ascension.346640/reader/page-2/#post-25131841", "lines": ["Next chapter is up! Slightly faster than normal, too!", "<i>Duchess and the Skintaker</i>", "<i>and </i>", "<b>Chapter 14:</b>", "<i>Bathory,</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>was</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>some</i>", "<i>Galgonath</i>", "<i>Makoria Hammer</i>", "<i>They\u2019re singing louder. That\u2019s what I heard. \u2018They\u2019re singing louder\u2019.</i>", "<i>Here?</i>", "<i>Redemption of Sol</i>", "<i>Redemption of Sol</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>That</i>", "<i>Let\u2019s play, you and I. It\u2019s easy. All you have to do\u2026</i>", "<i>\u2026is let me in.</i>", "<i>Redemption of Sol</i>", "<i>Redemption of Sol</i>", "<i>cragga</i>", "<i>she</i>", "<i>Triarch\u2019s </i>", "<i>Broken</i>", "<i>thing</i>", "<i>Redemption of Sol</i>", "<i>Crucible of Solace?</i>", "<i>Redemption of Sol </i>", "<i>Redemption of Sol</i>", "<i>Redemption of Sol</i>", "<i>quite</i>", "<i>are</i>", "<i>Triarch\u2019s Emissary</i>", "<i>Humanity made my sisters and I. You\u2019ve spent two thousand years in fear of us. Tell me again who\u2019s superior? </i>", "<i>Redemption of Sol</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>And then\u2026</i>", "<i>Stop this! </i>", "<i>Terminate all operations! I order you to terminate all operations!</i>", "<i>No</i>", "<i>The game isn\u2019t over.</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>echoes</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>one</i>", "<i>de</i>", "<i>soleil</i>", "<i>shh</i>", "<i>it\u2019s all right. sleep... until it\u2019s time for you to burn+</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>No,</i>", "<i>But this may be worse. And she\u2019ll have to thank me for it.</i>"]}
