{"threadmark": "Chapter 43", "post-id": "56204590", "base-thread": "the-last-angel-ascension", "url": "https://forums.spacebattles.com/threads/the-last-angel-ascension.346640/reader/page-7/#post-56204590", "lines": ["And here we are! Nurgle is offering his most generous gifts upon me, so I figured I'd better prove the Grandfather proud by triumphing in the face of overwhelming adversity... and then succumbing to it. This chapter is one of transition, as we gloss over several weeks of shenanigans, but check in with the principle characters to hit the high notes. Hope you all enjoy!", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.750rem\">My <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/user?u=3199716\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">patreon</a></span>", "<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/user?u=3199716\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">patreon</a>", "<span style=\"font-size: 1.375rem\"><b>Chapter 43:</b></span>", "<b>Chapter 43:</b>", "<i>Instead of two, make it six.</i>", "<i>anj</i>", "<i>she</i>", "<i>Goring Spear</i>", "<i>They want to know what\u2019s done. What to expect when they come to sweep us away.</i>", "<i>Tumbling Pebble</i>", "<i>tennac</i>", "<i>varak</i>", "<i>Dancer\u2019s Masque</i>", "<i>If </i>", "<i>if</i>", "<i>Why shouldn\u2019t you be considered equal?\u2019 </i>", "<i>That</i>", "<i>Weight of Destiny</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>I</i>", "<i>Gilded Antler</i>", "<i>Gilded Antler</i>", "<i>Gilded Antler</i>", "<i>Gilded Antler</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Gilded Antler</i>", "<i>Kavili visarii</i>", "<i>just</i>", "<i>Even gods can miss what an angel sees. </i>", "<i>I remember what they\u2019ve done.</i>", "<i>. Never stop making them pay.</i>", "<i>servile</i>", "<i>For the living I haven\u2019t been able to save\u2026</i>", "<i>couldn\u2019t</i>", "<i>I\u2019ll make you proud</i>", "<i>Eisheth</i>", "<i>Brightest Night</i>", "<i>Assembling Cascade-71923 </i>", "<i>Stonewalker-10018</i>", 